snippet.title: Muse Dash Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Muse Dash is a music rhythm game developed by PeroPeroGames and published by X.D. Network. It will launch in April or May on Steam, Nintendo Switch, Google Play and App Store.

Steam Page: http://store.steampowered.com/app/774171/Muse_Dash/

Press Contact: MuseDash@xindong.com 
Facebook: @MuseDashtheGame
Twitter: @MuseDashtheGame
